\c 34
\s Ezinye izibhebhe zamatshe ezimbili
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Zibazele izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe njengezakuqala\x + Dute. 10.1.\x*; ngibe sengibhala phezu kwezibhebhe amazwi ayesezibhebheni zakuqala\x + 34.28. Dute. 10.2,4.\x* owaziphahlazayo\x + 32.19.\x*.
\v 2 Ubusulungile ekuseni, wenyukele entabeni yeSinayi ekuseni, ume phambi kwami lapho engqongeni yentaba\x + 19.20.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo kungenyukeli muntu kanye lawe\x + 19.12,13,21.\x*, futhi kungabonakali lamuntu entabeni yonke; njalo izimvu lezinkomo zingadli phambi kwaleyontaba.
\p
\v 4 Wasebaza izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe njengezakuqala; uMozisi wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, wenyukela entabeni yeSinayi, njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* imlayile, wathatha esandleni sakhe izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisehla eyezini, yema laye lapho, yamemeza ibizo leN\nd kosi\x + 33.19.\x*\nd*.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisedlula phambi kwakhe, yamemeza \add yathi\add*: IN\nd kosi\nd*, IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu, elesihawu\x + Nani 14.18. 2 Lan. 30.9. Neh. 9.17. Hlab. 86.15. 103.8. 111.4. 112.4. 116.5. 145.8. Jow. 2.13.\x* elomusa, ephuza ukuthukuthela\x + 22.27.\x*, levame ububele lobuqotho\x + Hlab. 57.10. 108.4.\x*,
\v 7 egcinela abayizinkulungwane umusa\x + 20.5,6. Dute. 5.9,10. Jer. 32.18. Dan. 9.4,9. Hlab. 103.3. 130.4. 1 Joha. 1.9.\x*, ethethelela ububi lesiphambeko lesono, engayikuyekela lokuyekela \add olecala\x + Nah. 1.3; Eks. 23.21. Josh. 24.19. Jobe 10.14.\x*\add*, ephindisela ububi baboyise phezu kwabantwana laphezu kwabantwana babantwana kuze kube \add sesizukulwaneni\add* sesithathu lesesine.
\v 8 UMozisi wasephangisa, wakhothamela emhlabathini, wakhonza\x + 4.31;12.27.\x*.
\v 9 Wathi: Uba-ke ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, Nkosi, akuthi iNkosi ihambe phakathi kwethu,\x + 33.15,16.\x* ngoba yisizwe esintamo lukhuni,\x + 32.9.\x* uthethelele ububi bethu lesono sethu, usithathe sibe yilifa lakho\x + Zek. 2.12. Dute. 32.9. Hlab. 28.9. 33.12. 78.62. 94.14. Jer. 10.16.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Yasisithi: Khangela, ngenza isivumelwano; phambi kwabantu bonke\x + 34.27. Dute. 5.2; 29.14.\x* ngizakwenza izimangaliso ezingazange zidalwe emhlabeni wonke laphakathi kwezizwe zonke\x + Hlab. 77.14; 78.12. So Dute. 4.32. 2 Sam. 7.23. Hlab. 147.20.\x*; labo bonke abantu ophakathi kwabo bazabona umsebenzi weN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba kuyesabeka engizakwenza lawe\x + Dute. 10.21. Hlab. 145.6. Isa. 64.3.\x*.
\v 11 Zigcinele lokho engikulaya khona lamuhla\x + Dute. 5.32. 6.3,25. 12.28,32. 28.1.\x*; khangela ngizaxotsha phambi kwakho amaAmori lamaKhanani lamaHethi lamaPerizi lamaHivi lamaJebusi\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 12 Ziqaphelisele ukuthi ungenzi isivumelwano labakhileyo elizweni oya kulo\x + 23.32. Dute. 7.2. Hlu. 2. 2.\x*, hlezi kube ngumjibila phakathi kwakho.\x + 23.33.\x*
\v 13 Kodwa amalathi abo lizawadiliza, lensika zabo eziyizithombe lizaziphahlaza\x + Dute. 7.5. 12.3. Hlu. 2.2.\x*, lezixuku zabo lizazigamula\x + Dute. 7.5. Hlu. 6.25,26. 2 Kho. 18.4. 23.14. 2 Lan. 31.1. 34.3,4.\x*;
\v 14 ngoba kawuyikukhonza omunye unkulunkulu\x + 20.3,5.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd*, ebizo layo linguBukhwele\x + Isa. 9.6. 57.15.\x*, inguNkulunkulu olobukhwele.\x + 20.5.\x*
\v 15 Hlezi wenze isivumelwano labakhileyo elizweni\x + 34.12.\x*, nxa bephinga ngokulandela onkulunkulu babo\x + Levi 17.7; 20.5. Dute. 31.16. Hlu. 2.17. Jer. 3.9. Hez. 6.9.\x*, behlabele onkulunkulu babo, lomunye akunxuse\x + Nani 25.2. 1 Kor. 10.27.\x*, njalo udle okomhlatshelo wakhe\x + Hlab. 106.28. 1 Kor. 8.4,7,10.\x*;
\v 16 uwathathele amadodana akho kumadodakazi abo\x + Dute. 7.3,4. 1 Kho. 11.2. Ezra 9.2. Neh. 13.25.\x*; nxa amadodakazi abo ephinga ngokulandela onkulunkulu bawo\x + Nani 25.1,2. 1 Kho. 11.4.\x*, enze lamadodana akho ukuthi aphinge ngokulandela onkulunkulu bawo.
\p
\v 17 Ungazenzeli onkulunkulu ababunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + 32.4,8. Levi 19.4. Dute. 27.15.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Umkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo\x + 12.15. 23.15.\x* uwugcine; insuku eziyisikhombisa udle isinkwa esingelamvubelo njengokukulaya kwami, ngesikhathi esimisiweyo senyanga kaAbhibhi\x + 12.2. 13.4.\x*, ngoba ngenyanga kaAbhibhi waphuma eGibhithe.
\p
\v 19 Konke okuvula isizalo kungokwami\x + 13.2,12,13. 22.29. Dute. 15.19. Hez. 44.30.\x*, lalo lonke izibulo eliduna elezifuyo, inkomo kumbe imvu.
\v 20 Kodwa izibulo likababhemi\x + 13.13. Nani 18.15.\x* ulihlenge ngezinyane; uba-ke ungalihlengi ulephule intamo. Lonke izibulo lamadodana akho uzalihlenga; njalo kungabonakali muntu phambi kwami engaphethe lutho\x + 23.15.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Uzasebenza insuku eziyisithupha\x + 20.9.\x*, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa uphumule, ngesikhathi sokulima lekuvuneni uzaphumula.
\p
\v 22 Uzagcina umkhosi wamaviki\x + 23.16. Dute. 16.10,13.\x*, izithelo zokuqala zesivuno sengqoloyi, lomkhosi wokubuthelela ekuthwaseni komnyaka.
\p
\v 23 Kathathu ngomnyaka\x + 23.14,17. Dute. 16.16.\x* wonke owesilisa uzabonakala phambi kweNkosi uJehova, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 24 Ngoba ngizaxotsha izizwe phambi kwakho\x + 15.9; Dute. 4.38. Dute. 7.1. Hlab. 78.55. 80.8.\x*, ngiqhelise imingcele yakho\x + Dute. 12.20; 19.8.\x*; njalo kakuyikuba lamuntu ofisa ilizwe lakho\x + Zaga 16.7.\x* nxa usenyuka ukuyabonakala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, kathathu ngomnyaka.
\p
\v 25 Unganikeli igazi lomhlatshelo wami kanye lokulemvubelo\x + 23.18.\x*; futhi kakungasali kuze kuse umhlatshelo womkhosi wephasika\x + 12.10.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ikhethelo lezithelo zokuqala zensimu yakho\x + 23.19.\x* ulilethe endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho. Ungapheki izinyane echagweni lukanina\x + 23.19. Dute. 14.21.\x*.
\p
\v 27 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Zibhalele la amazwi, ngoba ngokutsho kwalamazwi ngenzile isivumelwano lawe loIsrayeli\x + 34.10.\x*.
\v 28 Njalo wayelapho leN\nd kosi\nd* insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + 24.18. Dute. 9.9,18.\x*; kadlanga sinkwa kanathanga manzi. Yasibhala ezibhebheni amazwi esivumelwano, imilayo elitshumi\x + 34.1. Dute. 10.2,4.\x*.
\s UMozisi wehla entabeni
\p
\v 29 Kwasekusithi uMozisi esehla entabeni yeSinayi, lezibhebhe zombili zobufakazi\x + 32.15.\x* zazisesandleni sikaMozisi esehla entabeni, uMozisi wayengazi ukuthi isikhumba sobuso bakhe sasikhazimula\x + 34.30,35. 2 Kor. 3.7. Mat. 17.2.\x* ekhuluma laye.
\v 30 Kwathi uAroni labo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli bebona uMozisi, khangela-ke, isikhumba sobuso bakhe sakhazimula, basebesesaba ukusondela kuye.
\v 31 UMozisi wasebabiza; loAroni lazo zonke induna zenhlangano babuyela kuye; uMozisi wasekhuluma labo.
\v 32 Njalo emva kwalokho basondela bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli; wasebalaya\x + 24.3.\x* konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayikukhulume laye entabeni yeSinayi.
\v 33 Kwathi uMozisi eseqedile ukukhuluma labo, wafaka isimbombozo ebusweni bakhe\x + 34.34,35. 2 Kor. 3.13.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa lapho uMozisi engena phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ukukhuluma layo, wasisusa isimbombozo\x + 2 Kor. 3.16.\x* aze aphume; esephumile wakhuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli lokho akulayiweyo,
\v 35 labantwana bakoIsrayeli babona ubuso bukaMozisi, ukuthi isikhumba sobuso bukaMozisi sakhazimula. UMozisi wabuyisela isimbombozo ebusweni bakhe, aze angene ukuyakhuluma laye.